Metrabs 3D Pose Estimation Model:

This addon utilizes István Sárándi's Metrabs 3D pose estimation model, which is licensed under the METRABS-LICENSE. A copy of the license is included in this repository (see METRABS-LICENSE file). Please ensure you comply with the terms of the METRABS-LICENSE when using István Sárándi's Metrabs 3D pose estimation model.

